oming months. Treasury officials are expected to announce an agreement on the terms of the federal aid on Tuesday afternoon.<br />\n<br />\nAirline executives spent this past weekend in discussions with federal officials. On Friday Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin told carriers that 30% of the assistance would need to be repaid, and that airlines would have to offer stock warrants on a portion of those funds.<br />\n<br />\nAirline industry officials had believed the money would come as grants that wouldn&rsquo;t need to be paid back. The government hadn&rsquo;t been willing to significantly alter those terms, officials and others familiar with the talks have said. It wasn&rsquo;t clear whether those terms changed in the agreement reached on Tuesday, according to people briefed on those discussions.<br />\n<br />\nDAL UAL AAL股東一齊集氣加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T04:30:23.000Z","msg":"文宣要人呀！！光復咗香港未呀？！共產黨打到黎喇 新界九龍香港無得避呀 (2.2)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/avpDkzU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/avpDkzU</a><br />\n<br />\n樓主借個位黎置頂可以嗎"},{"pid":"ef4e1950337c46c07511f942bd80dfa7fe84c7c9","tid":1972903,"uid":17866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"405ff2f13bd1e274d485c16d3e89e2cf6834080c","tid":1972903,"uid":4239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T00:50:00.000Z","msg":"波音沒份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T04:33:44.000Z","msg":"我啲BA 150 入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌佢老味"},{"pid":"4f79c8f7e301cf98081eb36765e9323ba654c523","tid":1972903,"uid":290025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T04:35:34.000Z","msg":"而家盤後升左10%但仲係跌左好多 點睇入唔入市？<br />\nDal 為例 而家應該冇太大負面沖擊 油價又大跌都有助成本。<br />\n睇好長遠既復蘇 但係咪應該等佢回返d先買？"},{"pid":"7a4b39849f5536